If you like to crunch numbers on a calculator, use this for a self-check on your spending and cash flow. If you prefer pencil and paper, we have a worksheet for you in our next section.
Getting your spending under control and in-line with your income is an essential element to building a healthy financial future. Use this calculator to analyze your spending (including what you pay on a credit card each month) to make sure you are not spending more than you bring in.
